# Unreal Engine C++ Project Git Ignore Template

# Hard folders/directories to ignore
Binaries/
Build/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Saved/

# Ignore C++ project files generated by Unreal Engine
*.sln
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.filters
*.vcxproj.user
*.sln.DotSettings.user

# Visual Studio temporary files and folders
.vs/
*.suo
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
*.ipch

# Rider / JetBrains IDE files
.idea/

# Visual Studio Code workspace settings
.vscode/

# Plugin-specific build folders
Plugins/*/Binaries/
Plugins/*/Intermediate/

# User-specific configuration files (local settings)
Config/User*.ini

# Ignore packaged builds
ArchivedBuilds/
Windows/
WindowsNoEditor/
Mac/
Android/
IOS/
Linux/

# Crash reports and local log files
*.log
